Edward Ellis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Ellis_(actor) 0 Edward Mayne Ellis (November 12, 1870 – July 26, 1952) was an American actor. He is best known for playing the title role in The Thin Man, as well as in A Man to Remember. Edward_Mayne_Ellis ( November_12_,_1870 – July_26_,_1952 ) was an_American_actor .
